"21:35:10" : {s: 21, a: 35, w: 10, r: "رجع", t: "تُرْجَعُونَ", l: "رَجَعَ", lc: 79, tl: "tur'jaʿūna", lb: "ফিরে আসা",e: "you will be returned", b: "ফিরে যেতে হবে তোমাদের", i: "kamu akan dikembalikan", f: 19, rm: "to return, turn back, turn off, (blame) upon any one, come back, repeat, answer, bring answer, be brought back. rajiun - one who returns. murjiun - return, termination. tarajaa (vb. 6)  -to return to one another."},
